author: gtully
msg: fix regression of https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/AMQ-2870 from refactoring of fix for https://issues.apache.org/activemq/browse/AMQ-2985 - unmatched acks are now stored as negative sequence ids so that we can differenciate between a durables that have acked messages after receipt and those that have acked because of unmatched. Unmatched messages are now deleted in the normal way
